{"type":null,"faqId":47563,"title":"手机异常发热 待机发热","answer":"<body style=\"clear:both; padding-left:10px; padding-top:5px; padding-right:5px; padding-bottom:5px\"><a name=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0019249765\"></a><a name=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0019249765\"></a><div id=\"body8539194\"><p class=\"msonormal\" id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0019249765__p28244554\"><strong id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0019249765__b9743886\">正常发热：</strong> 手机在正常信号下通话，发送短信，手机发热较少；拍照摄像、玩画面细致的游戏、上网浏览与下载图片文字，耗电和发热程度都会增加，这些都是正常的现象。</p><p class=\"msonormal\" id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0019249765__p52874399\"><strong id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0019249765__b20586118\">异常发热</strong>： 如果您的手机在某个时间（手机中部和电源键附近的边框）发热突然增大，或在您仅简单操作甚至没有操作时发热非常明显，续航时间明显缩短，说明您的手机有应用程序在额外的耗电。</p><p class=\"msonormal\" id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0019249765__p6107551\">异常发热的处理：</p><p class=\"msonormal\" id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0019249765__p54967961\">1.建议您进入“设置-&gt;省电管理-&gt;耗电详情-&gt;后台耗电应用”，查看后台耗电应用，并清理高耗电的应用，第三方卫士/管家类软件持续占用手机CPU资源或待机时唤醒CPU，容易导致发热和耗电快。</p><p class=\"msonormal\" id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0019249765__p24949608\">2.取消应用市场/应用程序/系统在wifi下自动下载更新或视频缓冲，可以防止用户在不知情时的发热。</p><p class=\"msonormal\" id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0019249765__p23219884\">3、若步骤1、2未生效，请重新启动手机，观察现象是否消失。</p><p class=\"msonormal\" id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0019249765__p7652366\">4、若步骤3仍未生效，请您备份手机的数据，恢复出厂设置。</p></div><div><div class=\"familylinks\"></div></div></body>","faqTypeId":133,"faqType":"电池与充电","useful":0,"unUseful":1,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"zh-cn_topic_0019249765","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Battery-Charging","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1445302183000,"seriesProductName":"P6 S-U00","visitedTimes":106,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"电池与充电","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}